# Apex-Indicator

Adaptive SMC Intelligence Suite built in Pine Script v6. Features HTF multi-timeframe bias dashboard, BOS/CHoCH structure detection, Fair Value Gaps, Order Blocks, Liquidity Sweeps, Volume Delta analysis, EMA touch zones, session filters, and an adaptive signal-learning engine with real-time accuracy tracking and full confluence detection.

## Indicators

### Apex Indicator
The main intelligence suite. Combines structure, bias, volume, and confluence into a single overlay indicator.

**Features:**
- HTF multi-timeframe bias dashboard (1H/4H/1D)
- BOS and CHoCH structure detection with adaptive learning engine
- Fair Value Gaps graded A/B/C with partial mitigation tracking
- Order Blocks with mitigation and OB+Sweep confluence detection
- Liquidity Sweeps with proximity detection
- Volume Delta analysis with trend tracking
- EMA Touch Zones with volume intensity overlay
- Snake EMAs (25/50/100/200) with head/body coloring
- Session and Kill Zone filters (Asian/London/NY/Overlap)
- Bias Flip Signals with cooldown and trend confirmation
- Real-time accuracy tracking for bull and bear signals

### Apex Candle Engine
Standalone candle analysis module with 43 pattern detection and FVG engine.

**Features:**
- 43 candle patterns across 1, 2, 3, and 5 candle formations
- Pattern-specific color coding for every pattern type
- Fair Value Gap engine with partial mitigation tracking
- 6 base candle states (Strong/Mild/Extended Bull and Bear)

